This paper deals with text attribute transfer, which is a natural language processing task, and proposes an unsupervised approach to solve it. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses a sequence-to-sequence model, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the proposed method involves iterative refinement, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions sentiment modification, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and formality transfer, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
